name: Austin Burke
profile:
What is up Flick Fans?!
I am a Rotten Tomato Verified & CCA Accepted film critic!
So this channel is all about movies. We talk Oscars, superheroes, Netflix, streaming, and we create tier lists. This channel is all about celebrating filmmaking. So I would love for you to take a look and see what this channel is all about. If you are subscribed, then I truly appreciate it. This community means a lot to me and I cannot wait to see where it leads.
I was able to get my start on Vine where I got around 140 thousand followers before it left us. Thankfully, I love YouTube and everything about it. Become a part of Flick Fan Nation TODAY!
